{
    "text": "Oregon Coast always hits like a different world \ud83d\ude0d  Home to ancient forests, glacier-carved mountains, roaring rivers, tranquil lakes, and grassy plains, this idyllic Pacific Northwest state has a bit of everything.  Have you ever been here? . \ud83c\uddfa\ud83c\uddf2 Follow \u27a1 @wandering.states \u2b05 for regular updates on traveling destinations. . \ud83d\udcf8@ryanresatka @somewheresierra @jguzmannn @glennleerobinson @josemostajo @wanderrlex @ryan_bangsund @trekkingwithb @frank.shoots . . . . . . #oregoncoast #oregonexplored #oregonnw #oregonlife #nationalpark #nationalparks #nationalparkservice #findyourpark #nationalparkgeek #naturefandom #travelideas #travelinspiration #travelphotography\ud83d\udcf7",
